* BrightBlade nodded and did what Manterorr commanded, after all, this was 
their base. She smiled to herself as she was being taken to Hell Beast, 
so...she would finally have a chance to meet this bot that Gangon was so 
loyal to.
BrightBlade thought about how this Hell Beast would look like as she walked, 
would he be handsome or down right ugly? She shrugged, she guessed that she 
would find out when she got to meet him.
BrightBlade smiled to herself slyly, under a commander's command she would 
finally be able to give the Maximals REAL trouble, but this time with 
backup.
As she walked she thought about all the horrid things that she could do to 
the Maximals while under Hell Beasts command, she was going to enjoy this!*
